      "body" : "Apparently to enable high-entropy ASLR [the image-base also needs to be set above 4GB](https://code.videolan.org/solaris/x264/commit/c01bf42117b811a0469f9f6c374f4a0daa98716d). \n\n```\n                 LDFLAGSCLI=\"$LDFLAGSCLI -Wl,--image-base,0x140000000\"\n                 SOFLAGS=\"$SOFLAGS -Wl,--image-base,0x180000000\"\n```\n",
