      "body" : "Hi,\r\nFor what it's worth, I submitted a patch that fixes the issue on binutils/ld side: https://sourceware.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=19011\r\n\r\n(Should you want a patch that applies cleanly over binutils 2.31.1 tarball, there's also one here: https://code.videolan.org/videolan/docker-images/blob/master/vlc-debian-win64/patches/binutils.patch\r\n\r\nHopefully that will be of use :)\r\n\r\nedit:\r\nYeah so it makes readpe very happy as far as aslr is concerned, but windows can't launch the resulting binary, so... oops.",
